dmca.title: DMCA Complaint from Blue Eye Incorporated
dmca.body:
-----Original Message-----
From: Your Name [mailto:legal@desikama.com] 
Sent: Monday, January 15, 2007 10:29 PM
To: Legal Response
Cc: Copyright
Subject: DMCA Complaint from Blue Eye Incorporated

Attn: Copyright Agent

It came to our attention again that your client desitorrents.com message
board has just violated copyright on our content. Please review the
enclosed pdf DMCA Notification complaint and ask the admin of
desitorrents.com to delete the infringing post from the message board. 

We seek fastest response regarding this matter. If you have any further
questions regarding the content in question, please email us.

Yours sincerely,

Aaron.
